  "title": "Geo-search box widget",
  "body": "In my opinion this is both a feature request and a bug.\r\n\r\nAt the moment we cannot use instantsearch.js to make geo-search with an easily defined. Changes Search parameters don't seem effect once mounted properly and changing the latlng wont give me proper results.\r\n\r\nDoes anyone have a way to use instantsearch that:\r\n\r\n1. geocodes a places location\r\n2. adds that as a center on the map\r\n3. Shows results based on _geoloc\r\n\r\nBoth versions of instantsearch are effected.\r\n- react-instantsearch\r\n- instantsearch.js\r\n",
